title: ADVICE: Grass Fire - Hackett
description:
There is a grass fire burning on the northern side of Mt Ainslie in Hackett. 
 
Crews from ACT Fire & Rescue, ACT Rural Fire Service and ACT Parks and Conservation Service are on scene responding to the fire.
 
Smoke and flames may be visible in the area.
 
No properties are under threat.
